Reasoning: 
1) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a method for detecting salient regions in images using visual cues. 
2) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel bottom-up cue for saliency detection, which involves machine learning techniques. 
3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of a hierarchical segmentation model based on Normalized Graph-Cut, which is a machine learning technique. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image analysis and processing. 
5) cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with visual cues and saliency detection, which are related to graphics.
